Package: wstats
Title: Weighted Descriptive Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Johann D. Gaebler", email = "me@jgaeb.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Weighted versions of common descriptive statistics (variance,
    standard deviation, covariance, correlation, quantiles) for importance
    weights. Computationally intensive routines are implemented in C++ via
    cpp11.
